1. *Studio* je opremljeno najsavremenijom opremom. (The *studio* is equipped with state-of-the-art equipment.)
2. Glumci će se sutra sresti u *studiju*. (*Actors will meet tomorrow in the* studio.)
3. Moja sestra je arhitekta i otvorila je svoj arhitektonski *studio*. (My sister is an architect and opened her own architectural *studio*.)
4. *Studijski* album benda je dostupan na svim digitalnim platformama. (*The band's studio* album is available on all digital platforms.)
5. Nisam siguran da li je ovo pravi *studio*, izgleda kao spavaća soba. (I'm not sure if this is a real *studio*, it looks like a bedroom.)
6. *Studirao* sam umetnost u Parizu pre nego što sam se vratio u Srbiju. (*I studied* art in Paris before returning to Serbia.)
7. Završio sam *studije* elektrotehnike pre dve godine. (I finished my *studies* in electrical engineering two years ago.)